Multiple provisions of my bill, the Better Military Housing Act, were also incorporated into the #FY20NDAA. Congress must ensure proper oversight of private military housing and empower military families.

@DLIFLC is the premier foreign language institution in the nation. I introduced legislation to expand its accreditation authority to not only provide an Associates, but Bachelor of Arts in foreign language. My bill was included in #FY20NDAA, Congress's funding bill for defense. https://twitter.com/MontereyHerald/status/1139296877579558913 …

I also included provisions to require a tenant bill of rights for residents of PMH; prohibit reprisal; create a housing advocate not employed by  private partner; establish an accounting of respective responsibilities of landlord & tenant; implement an improved work order system
Jon - This will impact all military families in and entering into private military housing across the country.

Thank you @RepJasonCrow for your leadership in incorporating our bipartisan bill, the Defense Language Improvement Act, into #FY20NDAA. Allows @DLIFLC to award a Bachelors of Arts degree in foreign language to support servicemember learning opportunities and recruitment/retention

Thanks to @RepAnthonyBrown for including a provision of our bill, the Better Military Housing Act, in #FY20NDAA. The amendment requires @DoD_IG annually review 15 randomly selected military installations for the oversight of privatized military housing & make the results public.
